803
00:50:32,463 --> 00:50:36,299
I would have liked to have continued
but nothing beats <i>Reality</i>.

804
00:50:36,341 --> 00:50:38,801
So I pretty much went back to work.

805
00:50:39,678 --> 00:50:41,137
What did you do?

806
00:50:41,221 --> 00:50:44,140
I... Well, I'd do hired labour.

807
00:50:44,308 --> 00:50:48,227
Demolition, renovation of buildings,

808
00:50:48,645 --> 00:50:53,066
of homes, you know. Restoration.

809
00:50:54,485 --> 00:50:55,818
Did you enjoy that?

810
00:50:55,903 --> 00:51:00,656
I do. (stammering) It keeps the blood
circulating, keeps you fit, yeah.

811
00:51:01,158 --> 00:51:03,493
But it's quite far away from music.

812
00:51:03,535 --> 00:51:07,413
Uh... Yeah, quite a bit,
quite a different contrast, yeah.

